### InsertContent — local function host
### Requires the VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client).
### Run: F5 in VS Code (or `func start`) then click "Send Request" above the request below.

@localBaseUrl = http://localhost:7071
@localFunctionKey =

### Local: send sample payload (no key needed when running locally)
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/api/InsertContent
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample-payload.json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Deployed function — fill in the values below before sending
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
@functionAppName = your-func-app
@functionKey = paste-function-key-here
@azureBaseUrl = https://{{functionAppName}}.azurewebsites.net

### Deployed: send sample payload using ?code=<function key>
POST {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/InsertContent?code={{functionKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./sample-payload.json


### Deployed: send sample payload using x-functions-key header
POST {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/InsertContent
Content-Type: application/json
x-functions-key: {{functionKey}}

< ./sample-payload.json


### Negative test — empty body (expect 400)
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/api/InsertContent
Content-Type: application/json


### Negative test — invalid JSON (expect 400)
POST {{localBaseUrl}}/api/InsertContent
Content-Type: application/json

{ this is : not valid json
